  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK263">
<l>tuṟantārkkut tuppuravu vēṇṭi maṟantārkoṉ</l>
<l>maṟṟai yavarka ṭavam</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is to provide food etc, for the ascetics who have abandoned (the desire of earthly possessions) that other persons have forgotten (to practise) austerity ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
